The AAR it produces bundles third-party components under their own licenses:

  - androidx/media (decoder_ffmpeg wrapper) — Apache License 2.0
        https://github.com/androidx/media
  - FFmpeg — GNU LGPL (built with --disable-gpl; no GPL-only components)
